   "source": [
    "# The Study of Music Influence on people\n",
    "This case study deals with the impact of music on everyday life,the way people interact with music and also the level of interest people have in music.\n",
    "\n",
    "## Ask Phase\n",
    "* What is the interaction of different age groups with music?\n",
    "* What is the distribution of users per platforms?\n",
    "* What genre do majority of the people enjoy?\n",
    "* Does genre affect the daily lives of users?\n",
    "* What percentage of the sample size is exploratory?\n",
    "\n",
    "## Prepare Phase\n",
    "The data used in this case study is an open source data available on kaggle as **Music & Mental Health Survey Results** by *Catherine Rasgaitis* for personal and also research reasons.We would be importing this data for analysis purpose and also be sharing findings in written form and also vizuals.\n",
    " The choice for this analysis is the R programming language and the various packages and library used are as follows:\n",
    " \n",
    "*  readr\n",
    "*  diplyr\n",
    "*  tidyverse\n",
    "*  tidyr\n",
    "*  ggplot2\n",
    "*  lubridate\n",
    "\n",
    " I would now go ahead and install my packages and also import my data for cleaning."
   ]
